741
00:48:50,243 --> 00:48:51,869
Aku peringatkan.

742
00:48:51,953 --> 00:48:54,330
Jika kau membuka mulut tentang ini,

743
00:48:55,331 --> 00:48:56,290
kau dipecat.

744
00:48:56,916 --> 00:48:57,917
Ingat itu.

745
00:48:58,001 --> 00:48:59,919
Kau sebenci itu
dengan kehadiranku di sini?

746
00:49:00,003 --> 00:49:01,671
Keluar, Berengsek!

747
00:49:10,138 --> 00:49:11,264
Hae-ri.

